OL,3,C'I was just alone' Woman says
OL,4,Cbefriending service changed her life
OL,6,FA woman from Ramsgate says being
OL,7,Finvolved in a befriending service has
OL,8,Fchanged her life.
OL,10,FPatsy Denne was introduced to Gill
OL,11,FRoss as part of the Good Neighbours
OL,12,FService run by Kent Coast Volunteering.
OL,14,FThe volunteer befriending service
OL,15,Fhopes to reduce the feeling of
OL,16,Floneliness and isolation along older
OL,17,Fpeople.
OL,19,FPatsy got involved after both her
OL,20,Fhusband and daughter died and she was
OL,21,Fstruggling with her own health issues.
