OL,3,C'I was just alone' Woman says
OL,4,Cbefriending service changed her life
OL,6,FShe said: "All my family had gone and
OL,7,FI was just alone with all this worry
OL,8,Fand death.
OL,10,F"Things were not going well at all
OL,11,Fwith me."
OL,13,FShe decided to sign up to the service
OL,14,Fwhere she was introduced to Gill.
OL,16,FThe pair have since become good
OL,17,Ffriends and meet up once a week to
OL,18,F"talk about everything and anything".
