OL,3,C'I was just alone' Woman says
OL,4,Cbefriending service changed her life
OL,6,F"Without Gill, I think things would
OL,7,Fhave been far more difficult for me,"
OL,8,FPatsy said.
OL,10,F"It gave me the energy to force myself
OL,11,Fto do things not just sit here and do
OL,12,Fnothing and it made me want to start
OL,13,Fmeeting people again and it worked."
OL,15,FJodie Nesling from Kent Coast
OL,16,FVolunteering said combatting
OL,17,Floneliness is important.
