OL,3,C'I was just alone' Woman says
OL,4,Cbefriending service changed her life
OL,6,FShe said: "We're social beings we're
OL,7,Fmeant to communicate and connect with
OL,8,Fother people and loneliness is just
OL,9,Finsidious and it's bad for your
OL,10,Fhealth, it's bad for community."
OL,12,FThe service is encouraging people to
OL,13,Fsign up to be volunteers as they have
OL,14,Fhundreds of clients but not enough
OL,15,Fbefrienders.
